gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Nuggets 120, Warriors 114
gameRecap.excerpt: Jamal Murray leads the way with 28 points, five rebounds and three assists as the Nuggets defeated the Warriors, 120-114.  Nikola Jokic added 26 points (18-18 FT), 14 rebounds and eight assists in the victory.  Andrew Wiggins led the Warriors with 22 points, while Stephen Curry added 18 points and four assists in the losing effort. The Nuggets have won their fifth consecutive game and improve to 22-10 on the season, while the Warriors five-game winning streak comes to an end, falling to 15-15.
